    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the third one, when they told us to go to a certain place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went into hiding then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], yes, that was called an [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 150 people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm the only one that survived from the 150.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I felt-- feel guilty about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I say to myself, why me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why did I survive from all that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but if I didn't get sick with dysentery, I would have been with the 150.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
